    <h1>20260604 - Lapu-Lapu GOCC and Japan</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"a7b3c1b16d7e" id=3D"id-20260604-Lapu-LapuGOCCandJap=
an-ApplicationMonitoringOnboarding&amp;DashboardReview=E2=80=93MeetingNotes=
">Application Monitoring Onboarding &amp; Dashboard Review =E2=80=93 Meetin=
g Notes</h1>
<p local-id=3D"ab4e4fb8021d"></p>
<p local-id=3D"b3d40f75806c"><strong>GOCC Dashboard for ongoing service and=
 responses to Japan-related alerts/incidents</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"b6e9dfebfa8a"></p>
<p local-id=3D"70497fd75b9e"><strong><u>Dashboards</u></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"d0fb5458ee43">Prod - <strong>Employee Experience Dashboard <=
/strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"77ce0270a2d1">
<li local-id=3D"d9051a5a5ebe">
<p local-id=3D"5f564c02ff39">David set up meeting with PS Team to share das=
hboard and also Branch Office monitoring</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"fdd5dbc8bef3">Non-Prod -<strong> Developer Experience Dashbo=
ard</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"426970a078e3">
<li local-id=3D"9a603cc2ad33">
<p local-id=3D"4cfbcdea01d2">Check the current configuration for Health Che=
ck email to replace current TEM work</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d4e66c1b256e">
<p local-id=3D"c84d79c9a14d">Decide what to do with alerts =E2=86=90 Check =
in with TEM Sangram and Rupesh</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"29e2fef75f55">
<p local-id=3D"c7cf9a4c7cd0"><img height=3D"250" style=3D"margin: 2px; bord=
er: 1px solid #ddd; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: text-bottom;" s=
rc=3D"00c6baf2885e49d972620f047eaf2a0683d1c6cde6e43ba34b1095d2aeeda7bb" wid=
th=3D"250"></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8043234373e5"><strong>URL Monitoring Transition to GOCC</str=
ong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"2de3763b6f7d">
<li local-id=3D"eeba575180c9">
<p local-id=3D"6b36084452c7">Jonan update Onboarding data source for diff c=
heck against SNOW to catch quality issues with the data.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"00209ec83326">
<p local-id=3D"eda6dd8e5878">Some Onboarding data has issues like strike-th=
ru fonts</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f18e998d0867"><strong>Branch dashboards and DC Minions</stro=
ng> - Comparison reports between nodes</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f64a3a021bca">
<li local-id=3D"c4afa575c668">
<p local-id=3D"9a838efdd487">OAR Team: <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"m=
ailto:debamalya_das@manulife.com" rel=3D"nofollow">debamalya_das@manulife.c=
om</a>; <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"mailto:edward_ian_vera@manulife.=
com" rel=3D"nofollow">edward_ian_vera@manulife.com</a>; <a class=3D"externa=
l-link" href=3D"mailto:jesusjr_pepito@manulife.com" rel=3D"nofollow">jesusj=
r_pepito@manulife.com</a>; <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"mailto:paula_=
segovia@manulife.com" rel=3D"nofollow">paula_segovia@manulife.com</a></p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"d54f9c041665">
<p local-id=3D"bf2b6210f481">Requirements: David put together PRD and send =
to OAR</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b384c0b41c1a"><strong>xMatters</strong> - quality report for=
 Japan</p>
<ul local-id=3D"13db92d0524a">
<li local-id=3D"90f8a5eed8cd">
<p local-id=3D"3ce7d91f5c8c">OAR Jonan/Edward engage vendor for xMatters qu=
ality control (Updated group and member registration)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"db6ec6528deb"><strong>SMS spam Incident</strong> - Monitorin=
g Team response</p>
<p local-id=3D"688319e6cd59"><strong>ADX</strong>: GOCC can check if FW ope=
n and agent is installed</p>
<p local-id=3D"394ad55293ef"><strong>File Share / File Transfer</strong>: s=
eparate from Lapu-Lapu for now</p>
<p local-id=3D"769350b1757f"></p>
<p local-id=3D"93e2b16ca031"></p>
<p local-id=3D"36478e9d4d23"></p>
